channel.title: Games you play?
channel.description:
Well, I'm wonder what kind of games people play, seeing as I'm bored and can't find anything to do.
I don't wanna hear RuneScape, WoW, or MapleStory.
There was this one game that I enjoyed playing. It was a sort of conquer/bandit game based in futuristic time lines. You have a ship, you go to planets, you collect resources, you get money, you conquer your own planet, you create a population on that planet, you gain more money, you get defenses, you conquer more planets. Eventually someone better or a "clan" comes in and takes it over for fun. You log back in, you find your planet conquered and some clan members patrolling around waiting for you to pop up. There is also space message beacons that display messages. I got "Haha. Noob".
I stopped playing :P I always wanted to play again though. I forgot the name.
